opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 1st day of May, 2015, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, the Petition for Writ of Prohibition is DENIED, and the Prothonotary is DIRECTED to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
